Introduction:
A web site that,s used to search for available or book tables at a restaurant
Scope:
The website should be easy to use and selectr the table that the user wants after reviewing the details of the table and service
Functional requirements:
Search functionality:
When the user searches for the table the system should give the available seats/tables for the user.
Table details:
When user click on a seat the system should display the details of the tables, which includes, number of members that can be seated, etc and price of the table
Check availability:
Then the system should show the availability of the table or show other available seats/tables
Check review:
Then the system should show the reviews and ratings for the table or the hotel for customerâ€™s choice 
Book table:
Then the system should open the booking page so that the user books the table
